The '''Independent Systems''' were [[Star system/Legends|star systems]] as yet unincorporated into the [[Galactic Empire (The Star Wars)|Galactic Empire]]. [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]] was one of the last remaining.

==Behind the scenes==
*The term "Independent Systems" appears in one of the earliest versions of the saga, the ''[[Journal of the Whills, Part I]]'' in the [[Alliance of Independent Systems]].
*The "Independent Systems" phrase was resurrected for [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] in the name of the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]].

